{"tid":875793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★支水呢？】屯門弦海今首輪推售175伙　傳大手客完全「失蹤」","createTime":"2018-10-25T06:43:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T07:51:37.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"18cad9d06efeadda76ed5c8fb71097d4ef7dc515","tid":875793,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T06:43:49.000Z","msg":"莊士中國（0298）旗下屯門新盤「弦海」今日（25日）展開首輪銷售，推售175伙。雖然該盤入場門檻折實僅288萬元，但市況不明，今日賣樓現場亦無往日「墟冚」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中原地產亞太區副主席兼住宅部總裁陳永傑表示，A組大手客時段未有買家出現。至於B組時段，市場消息指，暫錄70台B組客報到。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2011792/org/5efc193eb87a42a0090fbe7cc590efcf.jpeg/geVabuFw_Hs6LSBb9-AvVlZq8KWsbABdDUVuoQ1FbqE?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2011792%2Forg%2F5efc193eb87a42a0090fbe7cc590efcf.jpeg%2FgeVabuFw_Hs6LSBb9-AvVlZq8KWsbABdDUVuoQ1FbqE%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=f1a818fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/地產樓市/251045/一手也轉靜-屯門弦海今首輪推售175伙-傳大手客完全-失蹤\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%9C%B0%E7%94%A2%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82%2F251045%2F%E4%B8%80%E6%89%8B%E4%B9%9F%E8%BD%89%E9%9D%9C-%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E5%BC%A6%E6%B5%B7%E4%BB%8A%E9%A6%96%E8%BC%AA%E6%8E%A8%E5%94%AE175%E4%BC%99-%E5%82%B3%E5%A4%A7%E6%89%8B%E5%AE%A2%E5%AE%8C%E5%85%A8-%E5%A4%B1%E8%B9%A4&d=w%2BUZzSIMS1FTQuacT6qlJ2i1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=cd6f3125\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/地產樓市/251045/一手也轉靜-屯門弦海今首輪推售175伙-傳大手客完全-失蹤</a>"},{"pid":"3846474c75ca4552d245d3f3e3d14551686fea03","tid":875793,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T06:47:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea366cf80608f10d7c6677c90ffea3c03c9345c2","tid":875793,"uid":154725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T07:15:58.000Z","msg":"屯門 唔計"},{"pid":"3ccb5a0679fec5641e35b889b825393b0903c65a","